## Progression Notes

- When returning to an exercise (e.g., back squat in week 9), aim to beat your week 1-2 weights
- Track RPE (rate of perceived exertion) alongside weight
- If you miss a week, continue where you left off
- After 2-3 full cycles, consider advancing skill progressions

